## Known Status Code Quirks
| Scenario | Actual code | Note |
|----------|-------------|-------|
| Duplicate email on `/register` | 422 | `validation_error()` returns 422, not 400 |
| No API key on tools | 422 | `no_api_key_error()` returns 422 with `CFG_6001` |
| Login with unverified email | 403 | Triggers verification resend |
| Logout without token | 200 | Auth is intentionally optional on logout |
| `BasicInfoRequest` | all fields required | `city`, `state`, `country`, `professional_title`, `years_experience`, `summary` |
| `JobInput` in job comparison | `title` field, not `job_title` | |
| `followup-stages` GET | requires auth | Uses `Depends(get_current_user)` |
| Preferences endpoints | 500 if DB schema mismatch | `UserWorkflowPreferences` must be migrated before these pass |

