## E2E Browser Tests (Playwright)

The companion E2E suite lives in `e2e/` and is **separate from pytest**. See `e2e-testing.mdc` for the full pattern reference.

```bash
cd e2e
npm install && npx playwright install chromium
npx playwright test --project=chromium --workers=4   # all mocked tests (no server)
npx tsc --noEmit                                      # TypeScript compile check
```
